-- Cameron says News Corp must clean up mess as priority
-- 
-- Mon Jul 11, 2011 11:27am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/11/us-newscorp-cameron-idUSTRE76A41D20110711

 

 LONDON, Jul  (Reuters) - British Prime Minister David Cameron said on Monday News Corp should focus on cleaning up phone hacking allegations before pressing ahead with their takeover bid for BSkyB 

 Cameron said the company needed to focus on "clearing up this mess" before thinking about the next corporate move. (Reporting by  Keith Weir )